@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ibzgev(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.cos(v1)
    v1 = (tmp - ((v2 + 0.22 / v0 + 0.11) - wp.exp(v1 + 0.25)))
    tmp = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.97 - v0 + 0.31) - (v1 + 0.47 - tmp + 0.96)))
    tmp = v0
    data[tid] = v0
